Ikatlong palapag, lumiko pakanan.

758
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:43,680
Hindi ako sasama sa'yo.

759
00:42:44,760 --> 00:42:45,280
Bakit hindi?

760
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:48,600
Hindi ako pinipigilan ng guwardiya,

761
00:42:48,920 --> 00:42:49,520
pero ang mga guro rito

762
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:50,440
hindi talaga sila masaya na makita ako.

763
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,200
Hihintayin kita rito.

764
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,400
Sige. Aalis na ako.

765
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:10,880
Pumasok ka.

766
00:43:13,640 --> 00:43:14,480
Kumusta, guro.

767
00:43:14,920 --> 00:43:16,680
Narito ang aking mga dokumento.

768
00:43:17,480 --> 00:43:18,720
Qing Ye, 'di ba?

769
00:43:18,960 --> 00:43:20,080
Tuloy ka. Maupo ka.

770
00:43:20,240 --> 00:43:20,680
Salamat.

771
00:43:20,720 --> 00:43:21,600
Matagal na kitang inaasahan.

772
00:43:26,440 --> 00:43:27,920
Narito ang iyong bagong uniporme.

773
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:29,440
Salamat, guro.

774
00:43:29,680 --> 00:43:31,320
Kinakailangan ng paaralan na magsuot ng uniporme ang lahat.

775
00:43:31,320 --> 00:43:32,000
Bago ito.

776
00:43:32,640 --> 00:43:33,280
Pakipirmahan po rito.

777
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:33,960
Sige.

778
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,040
Pwede ba tayong mag-usap?
